raw_dialogue_text = "Wow! It looks like you have completed all of the test rooms that we have set out for you... (I mean of course I shouldn't be supprised...)
---
Now, that you have proven yourself physically capable of the strain, you will now be tasked with completing a series of tasks which involve our new technology.
---
The next couple of rooms will get you acustomed to using the RADIALS before we throw you directly into the thick of it.
---
Remember [color=red]red attracts[/color] while [color=green]green repels[/color].
---
The RADIALS are activated by proximity and will start pulling in energy when you approach them. Press RT after entering their range.
---
You may even be able to get an extra boost if you jump soon after activating a RADIAL on the ground...
---
Good Luck!"
